{"id":"resp_0e5619b094ff039d0169402b372fb0819f9725a0f5f49253b6","object":"response","created_at":1765813047,"status":"completed","background":false,"billing":{"payer":"developer"},"error":null,"incomplete_details":null,"instructions":null,"max_output_tokens":null,"max_tool_calls":null,"model":"gpt-5.2-2025-12-11","output":[{"id":"rs_0e5619b094ff039d0169402b377298819fb5d5a4bbc896a2f5","type":"reasoning","summary":[]},{"id":"fs_0e5619b094ff039d0169402b381914819f983afc5356d40353","type":"file_search_call","status":"completed","queries":["How does Catawiki handle import taxes, VAT, and customs?","import taxes VAT customs Catawiki buyer seller responsibility","customs duties VAT import fees who pays Catawiki shipping international","VAT invoice Buyer Protection fee VAT included Catawiki"],"results":null},{"id":"rs_0e5619b094ff039d0169402b3abc04819f8d571c805ea5675a","type":"reasoning","summary":[]},{"id":"msg_0e5619b094ff039d0169402b3d2c98819f9cb5f3f2ecc5c46a","type":"message","status":"completed","content":[{"type":"output_text","annotations":[],"logprobs":[],"text":"Import taxes, VAT and customs charges depend on where the seller ships from, where you’re located, and the final bid price. In some cases, we’re legally required to collect import tax (VAT/GST) at checkout on top of the final bid and shipping costs, and then transfer it to your local tax authorities. When import VAT is collected at checkout, you generally shouldn’t be charged that same import VAT again when your order goes through customs.

Customs fees are usually charged when the order arrives in your country, and as the buyer you’ll need to pay all customs duties, taxes and clearance charges required for import. If you don’t pay, the order may be returned to the seller, and you can’t cancel an order just because you don’t want to pay customs fees. For EU imports, customs may ask to see a commercial invoice, which the seller needs to prepare. If you’re unsure about restrictions or licences, check with your local customs authorities.

Read more in the Help Centre: [Do I have to pay import tax to Catawiki?](https://www.catawiki.com/en/help/buyer-custom-fees/do-i-have-to-pay-import-tax-to-catawiki), [Do I have to pay customs fees?](https://www.catawiki.com/en/help/fees/do-i-have-to-pay-customs-fees), [Who is responsible for importing an object?](https://www.catawiki.com/en/help/buyer-custom-fees/who-is-responsible-for-the-import-of-lots)"}],"role":"assistant"}],"parallel_tool_calls":true,"previous_response_id":null,"prompt_cache_key":null,"prompt_cache_retention":null,"reasoning":{"effort":"low","summary":"detailed"},"safety_identifier":null,"service_tier":"default","store":false,"temperature":1,"text":{"format":{"type":"text"},"verbosity":"medium"},"tool_choice":"auto","tools":[{"type":"file_search","filters":null,"max_num_results":20,"ranking_options":{"ranker":"auto","score_threshold":0},"vector_store_ids":["vs_67c1ca0297608191965f3ee81f367f41"]}],"top_logprobs":0,"top_p":0.98,"truncation":"disabled","usage":{"input_tokens":19101,"input_tokens_details":{"cached_tokens":2176},"output_tokens":517,"output_tokens_details":{"reasoning_tokens":201},"total_tokens":19618},"user":null,"metadata":{}}
